N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4203.5 - Termination of employment

State Regulations

The chairman is authorized to terminate the employment of
any member of the staff of the commission at any time after such termination
has been approved at a meeting of the commission. Notes
